Class Transakcja

java.lang.Object
Transakcja
All Implemented Interfaces:
CsvAble
public class Transakcja extends Object implements CsvAble
Represents a financial transaction in the system, which can be either an expense or income. Implements the CsvAble interface for CSV serialization.
